## Setup Instructions (XAMPP)
1. Clone or place this folder (`chroma-syslogsystem`) inside your `C:\xampp\htdocs\` directory.
2. Ensure you have a folder named `uploads/` inside the root directory (it will be created automatically upon first upload).
3. Open phpMyAdmin (`http://localhost/phpmyadmin`) and import `database.sql`.
4. Update `includes/db.php` if your local MySQL uses a password (default XAMPP has no password).
5. Access the system at `http://localhost/chroma-syslogsystem`.